      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/ecd19e/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2023-10-12T09:25:49.985Z",
      "cooked": "<p><a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/alex\">@Alex</a><br>\nI\u2019m using EliteDireto XR over Bluetooth. I guess it\u2019s Power Target mode. Also I\u2019m using external cadence sensor (over BT too).</p>\n<p>By pause + restart (continue) recovery I mean that after this cycle resistance of trainer returns to correct value to meet target power and I can continue workout.</p>\n<p>As for HR mode, I\u2019ve pasted three links to workouts. Two with target power and one in HR mode. No screenshot for HR mode as it was more straightforward.<br>\n<a href=\"https://app.trainerday.com/activities/652392316d551bc8fcda6b40\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Trainer Day</a> - this is HR mode workout.</p>",
