      "created_at": "2023-10-12T10:51:54.661Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I\u2019m using Android, I\u2019m software developer myself and I guess I can help with debugging. As for now it looks like there\u2019s glitch at every workout I\u2019ve done since start of \u201chome season\u201d, some of them similar to each others so I guess they are reproducible.</p>\n<p>In general random ramp-up slope steepness and behavior when changing gears is reproducible. Those \u201clinear offset\u201d problems are new and I can observe if they occur again.</p>\n<p>I guess I\u2019ll get apk with some debug info&amp;logging then?</p>",
